					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SRAM makes the designing of any product easier but more expensive. With DRAM and SDRAM you must have a refresh cycle in your design. I think that PSRAM is supposed to do this for you so you don't have to worry about it yourself and it acts like SRAM.</div>

